      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic vehicle! It's in truly good condition, showing how well it's been cared for over the years. You'll enjoy a smooth, reliable ride and a clean interior that still looks great. While it has a few minor signs of past adventures, it remains a sharp and dependable choice for any driver looking for quality and value!",
