    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, and while all major electronics work, the cabin definitely shows its history. It has been mechanically maintained to keep it roadworthy, but it is no longer in the showroom state of its earlier years.",
