    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid, reliable shape! It\u2019s super clean, drives like a dream, and has plenty of life left for its next owner. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed every mile in it, and I think you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. This example is mechanically robust, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already performed and a cooling system overhaul recently completed. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry, providing exceptional turn-in and communicative steering rack feedback. While the exterior shows light signs of use, the drivetrain and chassis remain tight, offering the visceral, naturally aspirated performance and 8,000 RPM redline that defines this chassis.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 36500.0,
