    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine, non-smoking environment; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the heated seats and navigation, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The engine idles quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. Recent service includes a fresh brake pad replacement and a cooling system flush. The tires are at roughly 70% tread, ensuring many miles of worry-free driving. This is a solid, honest car with a clean title and a complete service history, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
